{"tid":1015611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊擬擲11億入股「美版連登」","createTime":"2019-02-10T06:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T00:26:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"f2dfea0d2f516bd3371fb0158add621b961f3cb6","tid":1015611,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T06:57:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190210/20609716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190210%2F20609716&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=45c0bc62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190210%2F20609716&h=e01fafb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190210/20609716</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年02月10日 <br />\n<br />\n騰訊擬擲11億入股「美版連登」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190210/large/a1004a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190210%2Flarge%2Fa1004a.gif&h=80693f53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nReddit用戶狂貼六四相片，諷刺騰訊入股。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被指有份封鎖外國敏感網站的中國科技巨企騰訊據報即將豪擲1.5億美元（11.7億港元），入股有美國版「連登」之稱的Reddit討論區，引起網民非議，瘋狂上載包括六四「坦克人」在內的中方忌諱圖片，批評騰訊入股Reddit，擔心Reddit早晚失守，淪為中共言論打手。<br />\n<br />\n美國科學資訊新聞網站TechCrunch報道，騰訊即將投資美國流量第五大的娛樂、社交和新聞網站Reddit。據報，騰訊將投資1. 5億美元。Reddit這次融資額最多達3億美元（23.4億港元）。完成此輪融資後，Reddit的預期估值可能達到30億美元（234億港元）。Reddit是美國流量第五大網站，僅次於Google、YouTube、 facebook和Amazon， 活躍用戶每個月達3.3億。Reddit在中國被封鎖，具有諷刺意味的是，負責在中國封鎖Reddit的正是騰訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民六四相洗版抗議<br />\n<br />\n網民不滿騰訊入股Reddit，擔心Reddit早晚會像內地般對內容進行審查，瘋狂上載包括小熊維尼、六四坦克人等中方大忌圖片，諷刺中共總書記習近平即將入主，提醒網友小熊維尼因被指酷似習近平而慘遭中共查封的命運；趁習帝未下令封殺前，急急上載坦克人，以示抗議。<br />\n<br />\n美媒指出，騰訊入股Reddit，未來會令Reddit在中國設立分支，還是對海外企業逐漸適用中國式的審查，尚待觀察。<br />\n<br />\nTechCrunch/美國之音  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n郭文貴以太古城單位賄國安高層<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n被撤居留權　華富商向澳政黨追捐款"},{"pid":"35169585cc5f0045617bd7e9f56b3509dea2fd9e","tid":1015611,"uid":3454,"like":292,"dislike":5,"score":287,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:04:54.000Z","msg":"屌定先<br />\n乜撚野美版連登<br />\n同台狗一樣咁自大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc4e1e27b5378ece3bcf5b3b04b8cac66b7861c","tid":1015611,"uid":209663,"like":146,"dislike":3,"score":143,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:05:08.000Z","msg":"入股有乜意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班美國佬feel到個網唔妥自然有其他討論區出現<br />\n<br />\n到時候就自然淘汰中資討論區啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你估美國好似大陸豬咁咩唔用we7就冇其他聊天app"},{"pid":"9cea182166fe207faea1eaf5e5caf1cb5547eabf","tid":1015611,"uid":64944,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:10:56.000Z","msg":"韋拿踢法似我"},{"pid":"24c1aa1b7e6ceaa6ec7af781908b9420cb532cc5","tid":1015611,"uid":232185,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:12:12.000Z","msg":"美版連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴撚線<br />\n邊有道似呀，英文網起人底好嚴已經唔同"},{"pid":"0d8015752439881c859319dc60c3a04adb4458a0","tid":1015611,"uid":92376,"like":121,"dislike":0,"score":121,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:12:54.000Z","msg":"奧斯卡=美版萬千星輝頒獎禮<br />\n格林美=美版吒吒樂壇流行榜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71fafff6185dca3ddd80d820c3443891ef45cafb","tid":1015611,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:14:10.000Z","msg":"擬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7468d403581cafe1033855c0a38089749deb22d","tid":1015611,"uid":35221,"like"